{"tid":1995693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"議事論事: 本土恐怖主義？；「見薇知著」嘉賓：資深大律師陳景生","createTime":"2020-04-30T12:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T12:59:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fd5c397300e9b425ea8216be557e135d7202e186","tid":1995693,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T12:23:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vHdmTUddjgs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvHdmTUddjgs&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=95b23851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vHdmTUddjgs</a><br />\n<br />\n本土恐怖主義？<br />\n香港在2002年通過《聯合國（反恐怖主義措施）條例》（第575章），但18年來從未被引用過，近期保安局和警務處高層公開表示，正跟律政司研究以《反恐條例》檢控爆炸品案疑犯，但法律界對此有不同觀點。有法律界人士認為，部分反送中示威者的行為已達恐怖主義級別，絕對適合引用《反恐條例》作出檢控；但亦有法律界人士認為，採用《反恐條例》檢控爆炸品案疑犯，是「殺雞用牛刀」的做法，擔心會被當局濫用來打壓異見人士。究竟香港是否真的受到恐怖活動威脅？以現行條例去處理相關案件，是否已經足夠？<br />\n（編導：羅燕雲）<br />\n<br />\n「見薇知著」嘉賓：資深大律師陳景生"},{"pid":"9430dd5ffeee35c3222397e92acf7c4602cdd76e","tid":1995693,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b702fef135c2ea6233ffaabcc3e8319a757e465","tid":1995693,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9430dd5ffeee35c3222397e92acf7c4602cdd76e","tid":1995693,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src